metadata.name: Entropy Spiral 1
metadata.description:
behind pixels, what do we see?

endless patterns and structures surpassing our understanding.
a blend of order and chaos, lurking behind website pages.
a whirlwind of information, each data piece birthing new potential.

against this backdrop, we unite and diverge, our identities merging and fragmenting. we are living examples of the ceaseless web dance, asserting with every click that order and chaos coexist at each other's fringes.

the internet is inseparable from entropy, just as entropy is inseparable from the internet.
